<br />
&lt;pre class=&quot;code_block&quot; style=&quot;width: 500px; white-space: normal; margin-bottom: -30px;&quot;&gt;ns1.example.com 216.194.168.112<br />
ns2.example.com 70.39.146.236&lt;/pre&gt;<br />
<br />
Then you'd want to follow the other steps in this article about activating your name servers at your domain Registrar, and then assigning those name servers in &lt;strong&gt;WHM&lt;/strong&gt; for your reseller account.<br />
